o-Week Hold By Warner Bros. |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |accessdate=March 14, 2020 |date=March 14, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200314213142/https://deadline.com/2020/03/batman-coronavirus-robert-pattinson-put-on-hold-1202883443/ |archive-date=March 14, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"DelayedIndefinitely\">{{cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/dc/2020/03/25/the-batman-director-matt-reeves-confirms-production-is-shut-down-indefinitely/ |title='The Batman' Director Matt Reeves Confirms Production Is Shut Down Indefinitely |last=Perry |first=Spencer |website=ComicBook.com |accessdate=March 26, 2020 |date=March 25, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327011942/https://comicbook.com/dc/2020/03/25/the-batman-director-matt-reeves-confirms-production-is-shut-down-indefinitely/ |archive-date=March 27, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Variety: PossibleDelay\">{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/hollywood-productions-limbo-coronavirus-1203543478/ |title=Hollywood\u2019s Biggest Movies Are Stuck in Limbo as Start Dates Remain Uncertain |last1=Kroll |first1=Justin |last2=Lang |first2=Brent |website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |date=March 26, 2020 |accessdate=March 27, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326190222/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/hollywood-productions-limbo-coronavirus-1203543478/ |archive-date=March 28, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"DeadlineDailies\">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2020/04/the-batman-tales-from-the-loop-netflix-matt-reeves-interview-coronavirus-1202904102/ |title='The Batman' Director Matt Reeves On DC Pic During COVID-19 Hiatus; Unraveling 'Tales From The Loop' & Netflix Slate |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |date=April 9, 2020 |accessdate=April 11, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412175031/https://deadline.com/2020/04/the-batman-tales-from-th