on Racing|Palmer Tube Mills]]\n|align=\"left\" rowspan=2| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Dick Johnson (racing driver)|Dick Johnson]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Third-generation Ford Mustang#1983\u20131986|Ford Mustang GT]]\n| A\n| 159\n| 7th\n| 7th\n|-\n|align=\"left\"| [[Third-generation Ford Mustang#1983\u20131986|Ford Mustang GT]]\n| A\n| -\n| DNS\n| DNS\n|- \n! [[1986 James Hardie 1000|1986]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Perkins Engineering|Enzed Team Perkins]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[David \"Skippy\" Parsons|David Parsons]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VK Commodore SS Group A]]\n| C\n| 140\n| 25th\n| 18th\n|- \n! [[1987 James Hardie 1000|1987]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Perkins Engineering|Enzed Team Perkins]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|NZL}} [[Denny Hulme]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VK Commodore SS Group A]]\n| 1\n| 2\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|- \n! [[1988 Tooheys 1000|1988]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Perkins Engineering|Holden Special Vehicles]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|NZL}} [[Denny Hulme]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Tom Walkinshaw]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VL Commodore SS Group A SV]]\n| A\n| 137\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|- \n! [[1989 Tooheys 1000|1989]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Perkins Engineering|Holden Racing Team]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Tomas Mezera]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VL Commodore SS Group A SV]]\n| A\n| 158\n| 6th\n| 6th\n|- \n! [[1990 Tooheys 1000|1990]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Perkins Engineering]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Tomas Mezera]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VL Commodore SS Group A SV]]\n| 1\n| 161\n| style=\"background:#ffdf9f;\" | '''3rd'''\n| style=\"background:#ffdf9f;\" | '''3rd'''\n|- \n! [[1991 Tooheys 1000|1991]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Perkins Engineering|Mobil 1 Racing]]\n|align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Tomas Mezera]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[Holden VN Commodore SS Group A SV]]\n| 1\n| 65\n| DNF\n| DNF\n|- \n! [[1992 Tooheys 1000|1992]]\n|align=\"left\"| 